race.comment: The whole field has been struggling to win. TITAN RISING (1) was well below best last time but the start prior ran on well for a close-up third similar journey. Rates highly here on that run and in easier company gets a chance to atone. SAZERAC (4) ran a much better race last time when a close-up sixth. Same grade here and should be hard to hold out with a repeat. MOORAK MISS (9) also ran well last time with a close-up third in similar company. Placed only try here and among the main hopes. FIGHT FOR FREEDOM (10) has not won for a long while. Safely held last time but drew off the track there and can improve sharply from a better gate. RIPPA BUDDY (2) is fitter for one run back and can give a sight.
